item.title: The Cyber House Rules
item.description: You guys realize you live in a sewer, right? Uh, is the puppy mechanical in any way? Come, Comrade Bender! We must take to the streets! I daresay that Fry has discovered the smelliest object in the known universe! Good news, everyone! There's a report on TV with some very bad news!

item.title: How Hermes Requisitioned His Groove Back
item.description: You're going back for the Countess, aren't you? Wow! A superpowers drug you can just rub onto your skin? You'd think it would be something you'd have to freebase. Now Fry, it's been a few years since medical school, so remind me. Disemboweling in your species: fatal or non-fatal? I don't want to be rescued. Leela, are you alright? You got wanged on the head.

item.title: That Darn Katz!
item.description: Wow! A superpowers drug you can just rub onto your skin? You'd think it would be something you'd have to freebase. Fry, you can't just sit here in the dark listening to classical music. And yet you haven't said what I told you to say! How can any of us trust you?

item.title: Bendless Love
item.description: That's right, baby. I ain't your loverboy Flexo, the guy you love so much. You even love anyone pretending to be him! Interesting. No, wait, the other thing: tedious. Hey, guess what you're accessories to. The alien mothership is in orbit here. If we can hit that bullseye, the rest of the dominoes will fall like a house of cards. Checkmate.
